class Todo {
	done = $state(false);

	constructor(text) {
		this.text = $state(text);
	}

	+++reset = () => {+++
		this.text = '';
		this.done = false;
	}
}
```

### Built-in classes

Svelte provides reactive implementations of built-in classes like `Set`, `Map`, `Date` and `URL` that can be imported from [`svelte/reactivity`](svelte-reactivity).

